---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
	title="Refund & Cancellation Policy — Bodhic AI"
	description="Refund and Cancellation Policy for Bodhic AI digital goods and agent skills."
>
	<div style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: var(--space-3xl) var(--space-md);">
		<h1 style="font-size: 36px; margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);">Refund & Cancellation Policy</h1>
		
		<div class="card" style="padding: var(--space-xl);">
            <p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); color: var(--mute);">Last updated: 7/23/2026</p>

            <h3 style="margin-bottom: var(--space-sm); font-size: 20px;">1. Digital Goods</h3>
			<p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: 1.6; color: var(--body);">
				Bodhic AI facilitates the sale of digital, downloadable goods (AI prompts and agent skills). Due to the nature of digital goods, which cannot be returned once downloaded, all sales are considered final and non-refundable.
			</p>
			
			<h3 style="margin-bottom: var(--space-sm); font-size: 20px;">2. Exceptions</h3>
			<p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: 1.6; color: var(--body);">
				Refunds will only be considered under the following exceptional circumstances:
			</p>
			<ul style="margin-bottom: var(--space-lg); line-height: 1.6; color: var(--body); margin-left: var(--space-lg);">
				<li>The downloaded file is corrupted or technically unusable and the seller is unable to provide a working copy within 72 hours.</li>
				<li>The artifact severely misrepresents its functionality as described on the sales page.</li>
				<li>The artifact contains malicious code that bypassed our security scanners.</li>
			</ul>

            <h3 style="margin-bottom: var(--space-sm); font-size: 20px;">3. Initiating a Dispute</h3>
			<p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: 1.6; color: var(--body);">
				To request a refund under the exceptions listed above, please open a dispute ticket from your Buyer Dashboard within 7 days of purchase. Our moderation team will review the claim and issue a full or partial refund to the original payment method if the claim is valid.
			</p>

            <h3 style="margin-bottom: var(--space-sm); font-size: 20px;">4. Cancellations</h3>
			<p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: 1.6; color: var(--body);">
				Since delivery of the digital goods is instant upon successful payment, order cancellations are not applicable. If a transaction fails but money was deducted, the payment gateway (e.g., Razorpay) will automatically process the refund within 5-7 business days.
			</p>
			
			<h3 style="margin-bottom: var(--space-sm); font-size: 20px;">Contact Us</h3>
			<p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: 1.6; color: var(--body);">
				If you have any questions about this policy, contact us at:<br/><br/>
				<strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:support@bodhicai.tech?subject=Refund%20Policy%20Inquiry" style="color: var(--primary); text-decoration: none;">support@bodhicai.tech</a><br/>
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>
